title: Icon 10 years
body: I still dint get my icon for 10 yeary of riot and all of my friends got em

replies.body: Not everyone has gotten their gifts yet because they're still being sent out.  I'm glad your friends got them, but we're not done yet per our [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-).  Hang tight!
